title: New Orleans Diaspora
name: New Orleans Diaspora
description:
A Map by Yvahncm

As a native New Orleanian, I am dying to know where everyone landed after Hurricane Katrina...  I personally am in NYC, but I have family and friends in Houston, VA, San Fran, Indianapolis, Chicago, Austin, Dallas, you name it...  So if you or someone you know is doin it big away from the Big Easy, shout them out!!!  Let's keep the community together!

Also wanna keep tabs on all my favorite Nola places, from PRE-K!!!
